    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到 BattleTanks - Animal Wars！</strong></h2>在充满坦克和动物的合作动作游戏中，保护动物世界免受邪恶的鼹鼠！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage1.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>两种独特的视角！</strong></h2>无缝切换双摇杆射击和第一人称射击视角！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage5.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战役模式！</strong></h2>探索5个充满活力的世界，80多个任务，包括竞技场战斗、防御任务、横向滚动的挑战和解谜！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage2.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>具有挑战性的Boss！</strong></h2>克服你路上的五个巨大机械野兽的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage4.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最多4名玩家的合作</strong></h2>召集你的朋友，一起跳入沙发合作或竞技游戏中！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage3.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>街机模式！</strong></h2>与朋友在11种不同的街机挑战中对决，如<br>死亡竞赛、夺旗、摧毁基地、生存、决斗、轰炸、疯狂隧道、<br>Boss Rush等！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage7.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创建您自己的坦克</strong></h2>创建您自己独特的坦克，并使用其中一种13种致命武器！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061530/extras/TanksGifSteampage6.gif?t=1720955722\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 多个游戏模式<br></li><li> 有趣且极具吸引力的图形<br></li><li> 独特的战役模式<br></li><li> 街机动作模式<br></li><li> 3D像素完美地图<br></li><li> 80多张地图<br></li><li> 横向滚动阶段<br></li><li> Boss战斗！<br></li><li> 最多4名玩家在自己的沙发上<br></li><li> 完全可定制的坦克和武器<br></li><li> 有趣的英雄和各种敌人</li></ul>",
